manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: The pull string toys are sized for little hands to grasp and feature flexible, soft and smooth edges for curious babies to explore with all their senses. The moderate size is suitable for carrying in cars, trains and airplanes for travel. Fun and brightly colored ropes attract the attention of babies, Different colored ropes promote color learning When toddlers are playing with toys, they can manipulate and use them at will. Over time, strengthen hand muscles and finger dexterity to master a pencil or spoon. The UFO string toy has 6 brightly colored ropes with different textures and pulling difficulties, some of which are easy to pull and can be used for baby play at bath time. The fun shape is sure to make bath time fun, it will not fade and is easy to clean. Helps brain development, fosters creativity and imagination.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 18, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Amazing to grow with your kid all ages
reviews.reviewText: Bought this to entertain my 7 month son on a flight!The end of the strings are perfect size for their little mouths to chew!The pull string airplane is adorable and made of high-quality materials. It's perfect for toddlers who are fascinated with planes and love pulling things around. The toy's size is just right for little hands to grasp and play with ease.What I love most about these toys is their sensory features. The vibrant colors, different textures, and pleasant sounds create a multi-sensory experience that captivates toddlers' attention. It's great to see how engaged and excited they get while exploring these toys.From a Montessori perspective, these toys are spot-on. They encourage fine motor skills, hand-eye coordination, and cause-and-effect understanding. Plus, they promote independent play and creativity, which is always a plus for young learners.Overall, I highly recommend The Baby Sensory Toys' Montessori Pull String Airplane Travel Toys for Toddlers 1-3. They are educational, well-crafted, and sure to delight any toddler. It's a win-win for both kids and parents!
